{"id":181190,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011923/","date":"2011-09-24T03:30:35Z","modified":"2011-09-26T19:27:50Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/9/23","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a> <b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/villagers-riot-southern-china-over-land-dispute-082055936.html;_ylt=Ap7IANgfS.fnlfuFJTly_qsBxg8F;_ylu=X3oDMTQyOHM5YjltBG1pdANUb3BTdG9yeSBXb3JsZFNGIEFzaWFTU0YEcGtnA2YyOTY0MTk3LTJjZTktMzUxZi1hNGNiLWI4YjFhM2JjNGRkYwRwb3MDNQRzZWMDdG9wX3N0\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国南方农民因土地纠纷发起骚乱</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——几百名广东乌坎村民星期五抗议土地被强征，演变成一场骚乱，在微博上引起关注</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/09/23/how-high-can-they-build-the-wall-the-limits-of-the-great-fire-wall-of-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">墙能建多高</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国防火长城的极限</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然脸书、推特被封在墙外，但是国内类似功能的网站还是令监管者疲于应付。潘多拉的盒子一旦打开，还关得上吗？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/23/world/asia/rape-case-is-a-rarity-in-chinese-justice-system.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国司法系统中，强奸案并不多见</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——贵州一起“戴套不算强奸”的奇案，反映了在中国控告有权有势者强奸是件很难的事情</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8783588/BMW-town-crashes-in-pyramid-fraud.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国“宝马”镇的旁氏骗局</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——华东石集镇近年突然暴富，满街都是豪车，号称宝马镇。但是现在人们发现，这原来都是一场骗局</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>NPR</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.npr.org/2011/09/21/140633602/the-curious-case-of-the-vanishing-chinese-city\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一座正在消失的中国城市</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——四百万巢湖市居民一夜醒来，发现自己的城市不复存在，而是被分拆合并进了临近的三个市。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/09/23/china-a-debt-babys-photo-album-2/#axzz1YgaJo2vZ\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">图说中国：从长沙机场看中国基建投资的喜与忧</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——关于中国公共债务的讨论一般很抽象，但看看中国借债建设的成果，能让人更容易理解</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/jackperkowski/2011/09/23/chinas-economic-expansionism/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的经济扩张</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——正如全球金融危机为中国提供了在新兴国家增加影响力的机会，现在欧洲的经济危机为中国增加在发达国家中的影响力制造了良机</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《大西洋》月刊：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2011/09/new-us-ambassador-in-china-is-too-popular-for-beijing/245537/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国媒体指责美国大使过于受到欢迎</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——骆家辉简朴亲民的作风，使他在中国得到明星般的追捧，这让官方媒体很不舒服</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/geithner-talks-tough-on-china-ip-for-some-reason/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">不知</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">出于</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">什么</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">原因，盖特纳对中国知识产权发表强硬讲话</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他说中国系统性地偷取美国公司的知识产权。作者认为他的言论有些过头了。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/09/24/world/asia/china-questions-5-south-koreans-detained-near-its-border-with-the-north.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国审问在中朝边境抓获的五名韩国人</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——其中三名记者，两名研究人员，据说他们在拍摄关于脱北者经历的纪录片</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/09/23/south-china-sea-peace-zone/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南中国海和平区？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——菲律宾推动东盟国家在南海问题上形成对中国的统一战线。它提出让中国收回主权宣称，把南海划为“和平自由友谊合作区”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>MSNBC</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://behindthewall.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2011/09/23/7917211-us-envoy-to-chinas-top-priority-jobs-back-home\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">骆家辉表示，他在中国的第一要务是为美国增加就业机会</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——为此他将力争美国对华出口翻番，并吸引中国到美国投资</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《迈阿密信使报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.miamiherald.com/2011/09/22/2420234/anti-china-bill-re-emerges-but.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">反华议案重现，但商界人士称它找错了对象</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国国会周四提出议案，谴责中国操纵货币政策。但是在华美商表示，国会更应关注打开中国的进口市场。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-22/china-can-help-europe-world-economy-at-the-margin-pboc-s-yi-gang-says.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国和日本称欧洲必须先解决自己的债务危机，在援助问题上不会提供的空白支票</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/09/22/us-markets-bonds-outlook-idUSTRE78K6KS20110922\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国卖出美债的时机到了</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国期望中国现在就开始大量抛售美元债券，从而令美元贬值，刺激美国产品出口。中国也不想拥有这么多美债，但是其他国家的债券更糟糕</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/ieb/?fa=view&#038;id=45591&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新兴市场的突起需要一个新的世贸组织</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——以金砖四国为首的新兴国家快速崛起，既为世界带来更多的经济机会，也带来新的紧张关系，世贸组织要因此作出调整</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/slowdown-debt-worries-in-china-adds-to-global-anxiety/2011/09/23/gIQA3NMGqK_story.html?wprss=rss_asia-pacific\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对中国减速和债务的担心加重了全球不安</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——本周股市的狂泻，部分原因在于对中国经济降温的担心。人们不确定中国能否实现软着陆。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-09-23/china-s-squeeze-on-property-market-nearing-tipping-point-.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的房地产</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">市场紧缩</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">接近临界点</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>8</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月份</span></span><span><span>133</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个城市的土地交易量比上月下降</span></span><span><span>14%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，开发商资金出现断链现象</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.forbes.com/sites/ericsavitz/2011/09/22/investors-to-buy-1-6b-alibaba-stake-at-32b-valuation/?feed=rss_asia\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">投资人计划购买</span>16<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿股阿里巴巴股票</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——以银湖公司为首的投资财团作出这一表态，这说明阿里集团不会在近期上市</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21530139?fsrc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">招徕中国旅游者：有钱，爱玩</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然中国旅游者的足迹已经遍布世界，但中国的旅游业还处于初始阶段。现在百度和腾讯这类互联网公司也瞄准了旅游者</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/sep/23/china-sex-slaves-basement\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国男子因在地下室囚禁杀害性奴隶被</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">收</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">押</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——此人被控在公寓楼的地下室里囚禁六名妇女做性奴达两年之久，并杀害其中两人。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/indiarealtime/2011/09/23/india-and-china-responsible-for-many-of-the-world%E2%80%99s-%E2%80%98missing%E2%80%99-women/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">印度和中国要对世界上“失踪”的妇女人口负责</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据世界银行的一份报告显示，由于重男轻女思想的影响，发展中国家每年少生四百万女婴。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110923/ap_on_bi_ge/us_caesars_entertainment_china\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">恺撒赌场计划在海南开酒店</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——世界最大的赌博公司转向中国</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-5737745207824609114?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":994,"categories":[1],"tags":[15592]}